data.description: Discover the allure of this captivating canal-front residence, boasting a seamless connection to the Gulf of Mexico from its scenic poolside vantage. A haven for boating enthusiasts, this home offers swift access to Charlotte Harbor, making it an ideal retreat for both year-round residents and Snowbirds alike. Enhancements include a recently repaired dock and a solar-heated in-ground pool. The roof, electrical panel, A/C system, Tuff shed, pool pump, septic tank, and water heater have all been recently updated, ensuring a modern and worry-free living experience. Storm Smart hurricane shutters add an extra layer of protection, enhancing the peace of mind that comes with this property. Step into this 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom Gem with a 1 car garage, complemented by a spacious 20x12 storage shed. Inside, cathedral ceilings in the living, dining, and kitchen areas create an expansive ambiance, further accentuated by a bright skylight flooding the space with natural light. Artistic touches abound, with a charming mural gracing the dining room's plant shelf, adorned with tropical palm trees ready for your personal decor. The kitchen boasts matching white appliances, a pass-through to the lanai with pool views, and an inviting eat-in breakfast bar. Delight in the scenic backdrop of the pool and canal from the comfort of your dining room. The master suite exudes spaciousness, featuring a well-appointed master bath with a large vanity and a tiled shower. Throughout the home, tiled floors and ceiling fans contribute to a comfortable and stylish living environment. The guest bath includes a shower/tub combo for added convenience. The exterior is a paradise in itself, with a generously sized lanai offering both covered and sun deck areas. An oversized pool, hot tub (awaiting a new motor), and a pet-friendly garden fence complete the outdoor experience. Accordion hurricane shutters safeguard the windows, ensuring safety during inclement weather. The backyard transforms into a tropical oasis, adorned with fruit trees—mango, avocado, papaya, banana, grapefruit, and tangerine—alongside majestic palms such as areca, Christmas palm, and other varieties. Flourishing with colorful blooms including frangipani, bougainvillea, hibiscus, jasmine, orchid, roses, oleander, and Royal poinciana, the landscape is a celebration of nature. Conveniently located near shops, waterfront dining, entertainment, beautiful beaches, and golfing opportunities, this property invites you to savor the Florida lifestyle, be it for a season or year-round.
